                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.5294/593a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-03-22T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 22, 1935—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>45. United Press report from Arizona today states that the Arizona State
                    Legislature adjourned yesterday and that the alien land bills died on the
                    calendar.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
